<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑同调加法，是指将减数凑加上适当数字，使其与被减数的部分数字相同后进行运算，然后再调加上原来凑数的一种求差法。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">689-286=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">689-286</Run>
    </Paragraph>
     <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=689-289+3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=400+3</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=403</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>